summary: The video shows esports players, some wearing team jackets, interacting with cameras and an audience. One player is shown writing on a large board listing game titles, likely related to a competition. The group then poses with a trophy and individual smaller awards, smiling at the camera. On-screen text discusses what the creator would do if they didn't win, concluding with "I guess we'll never know."
transcript: Everybody want to know what I would do if I didn't win. I guess we'll never know.
